{"tid":1839890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護罷唔罷工，關人撚事","createTime":"2020-01-24T15:36:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T15:20:36.000Z","uid":313312,"like":10,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b2dcc627571dfbfd8de7b80b4829eab1eba6ce3d","tid":1839890,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講政治，講醫德，你收皮，受人錢財，替人消災，你驚死受唔到風險咪唔好做，你估你依家做義工？你受住薪同我講偉大？你含撚，大把工有風險，驚咪唔做。<br />\n<br />\n明知咁撚高風險都唔撚罷工，係閣下決定，但死左唔好怨。如果你係唔收錢，我同你講對唔住，保我中肺炎死全家，唔係唔該收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c47fcbaa5ef8e247f3724bea40db9ca72214860","tid":1839890,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c751929aa257d6b77d737fe35a38df8089947db6","tid":1839890,"uid":313312,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2dcc627571dfbfd8de7b80b4829eab1eba6ce3d","tid":1839890,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"唔好同我講政治，講醫德，你收皮，受人錢財，替人消災，你驚死受唔到風險咪唔好做，你估你依家做義工？你受住薪同我講偉大？你含撚，大把工有風險，驚咪唔做。<br />\n<br />\n明知咁撚高風險都唔撚罷工，係閣下決定，但死左唔好怨。如果你係唔收錢，我同你講對唔住，保我中肺炎死全家，唔係唔該收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"又驚俾人抄，又唔敢罷工，仲要懶偉大驚病人無人理，嘔心死，同黑警口口聲聲維護正義，其實為錢有咩分別"},{"pid":"c7da0c33270eb05a66a784e10821e131e71797f5","tid":1839890,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:38:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"6f6b9bdafde6f995c8750d1776c2c40e8b7d4779","tid":1839890,"uid":313312,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"見班醫護，包括我身邊朋友真係嘔心死，明明唔想返，但又驚抄，講撚自己幾有責任，幾偉大，唔捨得班病人。真好撚嘔心"},{"pid":"751daf2333f305bae3ded68aa5792d21fc9279ba","tid":1839890,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"得負皮，無人駁到，對唔住我講野就係咁直接，咁人性，咁現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc13a8418761f549f518af92cc20b36ab67ed324","tid":1839890,"uid":249924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以做外國文宣 話比其他國家知政府開門由香港人死 起碼比到少少壓力港共政府先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"73ea62560c3ac9c6c32e013b0372834cdf8d1fa3","tid":1839890,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc13a8418761f549f518af92cc20b36ab67ed324","tid":1839890,"uid":249924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:47:46.000Z","msg":"可唔可以做外國文宣 話比其他國家知政府開門由香港人死 起碼比到少少壓力港共政府先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"你可以做，但唔好諗住外國咩都幫到你，正常依個情況大陸人都會反，香港人仲可以忍"},{"pid":"37dc24e476f0f0e49a67c21391757c2fcca80c12","tid":1839890,"uid":5519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"其實所有紀律部隊都係 多黃？咪撚玩啦"},{"pid":"bd8fdf017a232a3e87d26980f8278765aef52dde","tid":1839890,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"人記好撚現實，死多幾個都控制唔到就會驚，到時唔叫都會罷"},{"pid":"b47c767c4a1b9f03e352ce947f03d3058dc17afd","tid":1839890,"uid":252292,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"如果又有醫護因為哩單死，sor9ry我唔會好似心痛謝醫生咁同情佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 包單好多人直情會覺得係自己攞嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要明白你地唔罷工，繼續跪喺度食屎，係間接害死香港人。"},{"pid":"f4468b767a0d289b4b96d785c009dddb3268dd49","tid":1839890,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"幫手推上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n「突發」工會主宰武漢肺炎同打工仔既命運！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839894</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"p